313
00:18:53,087 --> 00:18:54,213
Look at this.

314
00:18:54,589 --> 00:18:57,217
The son of a bitch Lunts.

315
00:18:57,392 --> 00:18:58,381
ALL CHUCKLE:

316
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:01,586
Let me tell you something.
