319
00:19:07,569 --> 00:19:11,164
With you and me
and all of us as its principal players.

320
00:19:11,339 --> 00:19:12,567
Orson.

321
00:19:13,474 --> 00:19:15,840
Exhausted as I am...

322
00:19:16,010 --> 00:19:21,141
