00:19:39,968 --> 00:19:43,495
You see, Betty, I believe it was Stanislavsky
who said to Max Reinhardt--

332
00:19:44,005 --> 00:19:48,135
- Ginny, what a delightful surprise.
- Orson.

333
00:19:48,309 --> 00:19:50,106
