00:19:50,278 --> 00:19:51,438
- How is baby?
- Orson.

335
00:19:51,613 --> 00:19:53,843
- Let me take this for you.
- Thank you, just--

336
00:19:56,050 --> 00:19:57,074
It's good to see you.

337
00:19:57,251 --> 00:20:00,118
- I'll be back this evening.
