00:20:20,141 --> 00:20:23,304
Forum scene. Gather we our forces.

346
00:20:24,445 --> 00:20:25,969
Coulouris, front and center.

347
00:20:27,348 --> 00:20:29,475
Where is that gloomy bastard?

348
00:20:30,051 --> 00:20:31,075
