you're telling me something I don't know?

385
00:22:16,924 --> 00:22:17,982
MAN SCREAMS:

386
00:22:18,159 --> 00:22:19,649
Duthie.

387
00:22:21,529 --> 00:22:24,259
- Hey down there.
