Wealth. Travel. Fame.

785
00:43:28,194 --> 00:43:31,686
I can take you to movies
that have all that.

786
00:43:36,536 --> 00:43:40,404
Orson's spending tomorrow night out
at Sneden's with Virginia.

787
00:43:40,573 --> 00:43:44,134
