00:44:03,963 --> 00:44:05,828
Aye, and briefly.

796
00:44:05,999 --> 00:44:07,057
Aye, and truly.

797
00:44:07,233 --> 00:44:08,928
Aye, and wisely.

798
00:44:09,102 --> 00:44:10,797
What is my name?

799
00:44:10,970 --> 00:44:13,063
