00:46:49,295 --> 00:46:50,819
I'll show you a dictatorship.

826
00:46:50,997 --> 00:46:52,965
Come on now, get in here.

827
00:46:53,800 --> 00:46:56,268
Anyone not on the ground
with a rag in his hand...

