876
00:50:09,128 --> 00:50:10,493
Yes, I'm sure.

877
00:50:10,663 --> 00:50:15,362
No. Really, I'm playing Lucius,
Brutus' servant.

878
00:50:15,535 --> 00:50:17,628
- You're not kidding me?
- No.

879
00:50:17,804 --> 00:50:19,135
We open Thursday.

880
00:50:19,305 --> 00:50:21,068
- That's great.
