to submit your story personally.

928
00:52:36,075 --> 00:52:37,940
Do you think she'd do that for me?

929
00:52:38,110 --> 00:52:40,977
Well, I mean, I can ask.

930
00:52:41,147 --> 00:52:45,379
Maybe she could just put it on his desk.
